    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/8288fba3b9b728b10d927f63b606b852.avif?t=1737960688\" width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let your imagination run free in this cozy bottle builder! Terrarium encourages the player to focus on the little things in life. Specifically, things that can fit in a bottle. Like mushrooms... grass... and lighthouses. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/e5f2153855508a549998fec3e2b97343.poster.avif?t=1737960688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/e5f2153855508a549998fec3e2b97343.webm?t=1737960688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/e5f2153855508a549998fec3e2b97343.mp4?t=1737960688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/a134fc27b6e0b4fad6d4dc2f9ee861a0.avif?t=1737960688\" width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FREEDOM! Build your diorammas with <strong>NO LIMITS</strong> <span class=\"bb_strike\">(Some limits may apply)</span>. With Terrarium's gridless building gameplay, player's can express their own creative vision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/f538f7c9f7ff8c5d666f8f763375ba8d.poster.avif?t=1737960688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/f538f7c9f7ff8c5d666f8f763375ba8d.webm?t=1737960688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/f538f7c9f7ff8c5d666f8f763375ba8d.mp4?t=1737960688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/01f9c046b438fdf4bd8c3f8e91755f2a.avif?t=1737960688\" width=800 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative gridless Build System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic key binds for optimal building practices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Available slots for all your build ideas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All new Play Mode to witness your creations in a whole new way</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy and atmospheric environment for a relaxing time to create your dream bottle!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Items, animals, and decorations to customize the bottle to your liking</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/6dd5b9b94b754ebeb6cacc884602db40.poster.avif?t=1737960688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/6dd5b9b94b754ebeb6cacc884602db40.webm?t=1737960688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262910/extras/6dd5b9b94b754ebeb6cacc884602db40.mp4?t=1737960688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
